<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>로그인 | 학사관리시스템</title>
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" as="style" crossorigin href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.8/dist/web/static/pretendard.css" />
    
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif;
            background-color: #EEF2FF; /* 부드러운 연한 파란색 배경 */
        }
        /* 좌측 이미지 배경 설정 */
        .login-bg-image {
            background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1562774053-701939374585?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
        }
        /* 이미지 위 오버레이 그라데이션 */
        .overlay-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.4), rgba(23, 37, 84, 0.8));
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4">

    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden flex w-full max-w-5xl h-[650px]">
        
        <div class="hidden lg:block lg:w-1/2 relative login-bg-image">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 overlay-gradient"></div>
            
            <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-10 text-white z-10">
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">학사관리시스템</h1>
                <p class="text-gray-200 font-light tracking-wide opacity-80">Academic Management System</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center px-12 py-10 bg-white relative">
            
            <div class="text-center mb-10">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-blue-600 rounded-full mb-4 shadow-lg shadow-blue-200">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-graduation-cap text-2xl text-white"></i>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">학사관리시스템</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-500 mt-1 text-sm">로그인하여 시작하세요</p>
            </div>

            <form action="/loginForm" method="POST" class="space-y-5">
                
                <div>
                    <label for="userId" class="block text-xs font-bold text-gray-700 mb-1.5 ml-1">학번</label>
                    <input type="text" id="userId" name="userId" placeholder="학번을 입력하세요" 
                           class="w-full px-4 py-3.5 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg text-sm text-gray-800 placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all"
                           required>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <label for="password" class="block text-xs font-bold text-gray-700 mb-1.5 ml-1">비밀번호</label>
                    <input type="password" id="userPassword" name="userPassword" placeholder="비밀번호를 입력하세요" 
                           class="w-full px-4 py-3.5 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg text-sm text-gray-800 placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all"
                           required>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" 
                        class="w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-3.5 rounded-lg shadow-md shadow-blue-200 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 mt-2">
                    로그인
                </button>

                <div class="text-center mt-4">
                    <a href="#" class="text-xs text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium hover:underline">비밀번호 찾기</a>
                </div>
            </form>

            <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-gray-100 text-center">
                <p class="text-[11px] text-gray-400 mb-1">테스트 계정: admin (관리자) / 20240001 (학생)</p>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-[11px] text-gray-400 mb-1">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-phone text-[10px]"></i> 문의사항 안내: 02-000-0000
                </div>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-300">© 2025 학사관리시스템. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>